# a\(n\) is the sum of the 4th power of the first A125907\(n\) primes\.

## Python
```Python
sum = 0
for n in range(1,10000000000001):
    sum += pow(prime[n],4)
    if sum % n == 0:
        print(n, prime[n], sum, (sum // n))
```
